  "title": "QUANTITY SURVEYOR (MECHANICAL & ELECTRICAL)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong></p><ul><li>Tabulate quantities, estimate costs and request for quotation</li><li>Knowledge of electrical products and costing</li><li>Updating contract documents, drawings and correspondences</li><li>Submission of progress claims and site valuations</li><li>Preparation of Variation Order for submission</li><li>Liaise with subcontractors and clients</li><li>Ensure timely completion of an assign tender</li></ul><p><br />\n<strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Candidates must possess at least a Diploma / Degree in Quantity Survey or Engineering or equivalent</li><li>Minimum 2 years of QS experience or fresh graduate are welcome to apply</li><li>Preferable with relevant experience in Electrical Engineering Firm</li><li>Computer skills- Microsoft office skill (Excel, Words. Autocad… etc.)</li><li>Must be able to communicate in English</li><li>Independent, resourceful, pro-active and responsible</li><li>Work under tight timeline</li><li>Must be team player</li></ul>",
